Dialogs.Dialog: Ah... this. I picked up a wallet.
Want to find the owner together? Does it have a name somewhere?
We have to the owner right away. Meanwhile, let's go to the staff room and ask around.
That's right... I will deliver it to the staff room.
I seems the owner of this wallet is someone from my class.
That's so... I'm glad we could find the owner.
That's right, it's all because you picked it up, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
...After all, I couldn't find the owner.
No... I delivered it to the staff room, so I'm sure they'll find it soon.
Ah... I think it's good to wash the cleaning equipment sometimes, so I tried to move it, but it's heavy.
Is it okay?... Then, I wonder if tomorrow is okay. Can I ask you then?
I think it's better if it's clean...
（I promised to help▲高嶺＊＊▲ to clean up...）
Yup. Let the heavy work with me.
Huh, that's a cleaning tool case...
It's fine, I managed to carry it by myself. Don't worry.
Umm... Can you bring me the survey for improving club activities? I was asked by the sensei to collect it...
Is it okay to skip it?
I'm sorry, I'll do it. Wait a little more.
That so... Okay, I'll call you again.
Can I skip it? I don't think everyone has done it.
That so... Yes, it's not mandatory.
（What should I do about the survey▲高嶺＊＊▲ asked me about）
（▲高嶺＊＊▲ told me about the survey, but I haven't written it yet...）
Thank you for your survey, I'll submit to the sensei.
Yes, I'll leave it to you.
I hope you improvement plan is adopted.
Huh... What happened with the survey?
Ah... I'm sorry! I couldn't write after all...
▲高嶺＊＊▲? You're staring at your phone, what's wrong?
Ah~... Huh, I want to send a photo with an email, but I don't know what to do...
I know a little about it, can you show it to me?
...Yes. If you send it as it is, it's okay.
Thank you. It's amazing even if you don't own it.
Well, every phone is similar, so no big deal.
Is that so? Hmm... Can I ask how to use it again?
You should read the manual, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Maybe that way you can understand it, right?
It's not so difficult, so it's okay.
（That's right,▲高嶺＊＊▲ said she would like to learn how to use her phone. I would go see her）
（▲高嶺＊＊▲, I wonder if she learnt how to use her phone. I should ask her）
I'm sorry... Thank you for kindly teaching me.
I feel I'm somehow better at using mobile phones.
...Ah, I'm sorry. Teaching me how to use a mobile phone is a hassle, after all.
Emm... sorry. Somehow, our timings did not match.
No, it's fine. I know I'm not good.
Emm... I thought I'd keep cleaning the equipment little by little.
I don't you have to do it alone. I'll help you.
I don't know if I'll be of any help, but I'm from the same club. Let me help you.
Thank you... I think it will take a while, but... I think we'll be okay.
No, I like doing this... Don't worry.
（Speaking of which, ▲高嶺＊＊▲ told me about the equipment maintenance last time...）
Thank you, I think this is the end.
Good work. Thank you for helping me... I ended faster than I expected.
Huh... I've finished clearing the equipment. It's alright now.
Oh, yes... I'm sorry, I didn't help much.
No. I intended to do it alone since the beginning.
Hmm, ▲高嶺＊＊▲? Do you have any trouble?
I have a print the sensei asked me to collect, but I can't find it.
Then, why don't we look for it together?
Leave it to me. I'll go look around the school.
Yes... I'll try to find it.
（The print▲高嶺＊＊▲ said, where I can find it...）
Is this the print you're looking for?
I'm glad. Be careful not to drop it anymore.
Yes. Hmm, thank you so much.
The print I was looking for...
Ah, that's right... Sorry, what happened?
I see... I'm sorry I didn't help.
Umm, my new shoes don't fit well... If you'd like, could you be in the rally for a while?
I can't do it... I'm sorry.
It's better to rely on good people.
（By the way, today I was going to practice with ▲高嶺＊＊▲...）
Thank you, it seems that I have gotten used to my shoes.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲ seems to have more energy to spare...）
I'm sorry, I couldn't deal with it...
It's okay, I can do it alone sometimes.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, haven't you been getting late home recently?
Emm, I had an errand to do after classes... my way back was a little weird.
I see, I'll send it for you. Unless it's annoying.
That's not it... are you sure?
Yes... Then, thank you for helping me.
（By the way, I promised ▲高嶺＊＊▲ to help her...）
Thank you for sending it. You saved me.
No, I'm able to feel relieved each day.
Then it was worth it helping you. I'm glad.
Huh, you primised to send it... Did you do it?
It can wait until later, right? Sorry...
▲高嶺＊＊▲, is that a practice menu for our juniors?
I was asked to do it this time. I'm currently thinking about things to do.
I can help you with anything.
Is there anything I can do? make copies or anything.
Well then... It would be nice if we could try the practice menu together.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, I think you can assemble a good menu.
Do your best for our juniors.
（By the way, I promised to help practice the menu created by ▲高嶺＊＊▲...）
（I'm going to go practice with▲高嶺＊＊▲ today...）
How was the practice menu for our juniors?
I think the balance is better because of the improvements you did.
Really? I'm glad. Then, we should go with this.
No, it's thanks to you that I could improve it. Thank you.
You're welcome. It was a good training for me.
The practice menu for the juniors...
Ah... I'm sorry, I couldn't help you.
...I'll be fine, I'll try again next time.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, what's wrong? It looks like you're worried about something.
Oh... I'm thinking of giving a gift to Papa, but it's hard to find something for men.
Well then, I'll give you some advice. I think I can help you.
Is that okay? That's a big help...
Don't worry about it, I'll show you a good store.
I hope you can find a good gift for your dad.
（By the way, today I promised▲高嶺＊＊▲ I would give her some advice on present for her father）
（Today I promised▲高嶺＊＊▲ to help her decide for a gift ... I wonder what would be better）
Papa was very pleased with his gift.
It was thanks to your advice. Thank you.
Umm. The gift for Papa... I ended up asking Mama.
It was Papa's favorite... I should gave talked to Mama from the beginning...
Huh,▲高嶺＊＊▲, did you change your racket?
No, it seems to have been replaced... the girls' club knows nothing about it, so I wonder if the boys know...
Then I'll ask in the mens' club.
I know how to do talk to them, leave it to me.
Right, if you ask everyone in there, you will get it back.
（That's right, I have to ask for ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s racket...）
Thank you for finding my racket. The one who took it, returned it to me.
Yes, it was in the men's club after all. I'm glad to hear it.
Yes... Thank you for listening to me.
It's not a big deal, you're welcome.
Did you hear something about my racket?
It's okay... It's mine, I'll ask myself.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, aren't you going early to school lately? Are you on duty?
That's right. I'm on duty to water the garden pots...
It's hard to get up early
Eh... Can I go with you during your turn?
Sometimes I want to get up early, and feel like an honor student.
That's your reason? Then... Is it okay?
Getting up early to water the plants... sounds tough.
Not much, I think it's better to do it before everyone goes to school.
（By the way, I promised to go to school with▲高嶺＊＊▲...）
（I need to go to school with ▲高嶺＊＊▲ today...）
We've been going out at early morning, how are you doing?
I'm getting used to it. It feels good to get up early.
Fufu, right? But today my duty is over.
It was fun becasue we went to school together. Thank you.
I guess it was hard to get up early.
I was on duty after all.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, what are you doing so late?
Emm... I was practicing to improve my form.
Um, if you'd like... can I meet you tomorrow?
If you don't mind, I'll look at it, but you should ask a more advanced person.
Well then, I look forward to it.
It's important to improve on your form, but... I can't take responsibility.
It's not that a big deal, but... Yes, I understand.
You should ask a more advanced person.
（By the way, I promised to meet ▲高嶺＊＊▲ for practice...）
（I was supposed to meet ▲高嶺＊＊▲ today...）
Go to the club room first
Thank you for helping me improving my form.
Yes, I think I'm getting better. All thank to your help.
I hope you see the results of it in a match...
I'm sorry... I couldn't live up to your expectations.
It's okay, because I was just thinking sweet things.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, you've been particularly keen on practice lately.
Yes, I like to train in the park at night to get it right, but I was told I shouldn't go alone...
Want me to go with you? That way you won't be alone.
That's fine, but... I wonder what I should tell Papa...
Isn't it okay to tell him "I'm going with a friend"?
Well, it's decided. Let's work together.
（By the way, I promise to go practice with▲高嶺＊＊▲...）
（I'm going to help▲高嶺＊＊▲ practice today...）
Thank you for taking the time to help me practice. I was able to train as much as I wanted, and it was fun.
It was fun indeed... and you're amazing, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
It was thanks to you I could have fun. I don't think I could do this alone.
It is, thank you very much.
It seems the training wasn't as effective as I expected.
No, it's because I couldn't do it properly.
Umm, I'm thinking of making homemade sweets in my friend's birthday.
If you'd like, can you taste the prototype?
Well then, are you sure you want me to try?
Is that so? Since it's a prototype, it may be a failure...
Fufu, it's okay, I don't make things that can't be eaten. Then, I'm counting on you.
Oh, I don't want to force you to do it... I'm sorry.
I'm sorry, I don't think I can help you.
（Speaking of that, ▲高嶺＊＊▲ asked me to try some sweets...）
（I have to try some of ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s sweets today...）
How about this one? Is this all right?
Yes, this finished product will be popular even if it's put out in a store!
Really? Thank you for your advice.
Thank you. Will you eat it if I make it next time?
No, it's alright, I'll do my best.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲... how should I talk to you?）
（I'll call her differently this time. By her last name, first name, or a suffix...）
Are you alone? If you'd like, can you join me...
Huh... I'm in a hurry... sorry.
（I was refused, but is it okay to call her this way）
（I failed... I wonder how should I call her）
Hey, let's go together if you'd like.
（I think it's okay to call her like this）
（Wait, am I getting a little too friendly?）
（I think it's okay to call her like this）
I'm glad I found you, let's go together.
（I think it's okay to call her like this）
Whassup, why don't we go back together?
（I think it's okay to call her like this）
I'm sorry for surprising you... were you watching something?
It was just a little errant...
I was just trying to call out an acquaintance...
Ah... sorry, I didn't mean to disturb you... See you.
Don't worry about it. See you.
Emm, I was just trying to speak with someone...
...I was getting in the way. I'm sorry, I'll go now...
Actually, I was looking for you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Was that right? What do you need of me?
Thank you. You saved me, because I didn't listened to the sensei.
Are you okay? Well then, I'll help you out.
Me? But... Am I in the way? Well then.
That so... I'm sorry, okay? See you.
（Should I try to talk to her?）
Eh, I'm sorry... Did I surprise you so much?
I have to meet with an acquaintance...
That so... sorry for bothering you, okay? See you.
I was thinking of calling out a friend...
I see, that was it... I'm sorry, see you.
...You're the one I was looking for,▲高嶺＊＊▲.
I was in trouble because I didn't know the schedule for club activities.
Ah, I'll gladly help. Feel free to ask me again, okay? See you.
Huh... If you call people so loudly, you will bother someone, okay? See you....
Sorry, I'm in a hurry now.
Is that so? Sorry for calling you.
（▲小早川＊▲ doesn't seem to be here anymore...）
（▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ doesn't seem to be here anymore...）
（Would she be surprised if I call her out?）
Emm... I have something to do...
Well then, I have to go early. Sorry.
I wanted to see her for a little while. It's not a big deal, though.
I see... I'm sorry. I'll go then.
Ah... You don't have to apologize...
I was looking for you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Ah, you saved me. I knew it, it was best to ask you ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Feel free to ask me anytime. See you.
Huh... Next time, okay? I'm sorry.
I have something to do... I'll be going now.
That so... Well then, see you later?
I don't have anything special to do...
Actually, I have a little errand to do...
I'm sorry, I won't disturb you, then.
I... Was I in your way? I'm sorry... Well then, see you.
I was looking for you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲... I think it's a coincidence.
Eh, so that was it. Thank you.
You're welcome. Then, I'll be going now, okay?
... I wonder if I'm in the way... Um... See you later.
Huh, are you in a hurry? I'm sorry, I didn't notice. Well then, see you.
I'm okay. I'm late, so I'll be going now, okay?
I'm glad. I'll be late, so I'm going now, okay?
Yes, I have to hurry too! See you.
▲高嶺＊＊▲!? Are you okay? I have to hurry.
Yes... I'm okay. Um... I'm going now, I'm in a hurry.
Huh... Yes. Don't worry, it's fine... I'll have to go now.
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. ▲高嶺＊＊▲, this class is next?
Emm, I thought this was a class we had together.
Fufu, this class is different. See ya.
I see, It's a coincidence, this class has changed classrooms.
Is that so? I wish we had a class together.
Ah... Well, it would be fun... I have to go now.
I see, then go before you're late for class.
... Don't relax too much, or you'll be late for class.
It's true, I'll see you later.
Emm... Ah, it's bad. I have to go!
Ah... I have to go too. Let's do our best!
Thank you for picking it up.
I saw you because you were running.
No... Ah, is it okay if you don't hurry? I'll be going ahead.
Thank you for picking it up! I have to hurry now.
Thank you for picking it up.
I happened to be passing by. Well then, I'll be going.
You picked it up, thank you.
（Huh? ▲高嶺＊＊▲ seems to be over there...）
Huh... It's me, why are you so surprised?
There was a person who looked like you,▲高嶺＊＊▲... That's why.
Fufu, that's a mistake. See you.
（Ah~ I really thought she was her...）
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Wasn't you over there just now?
Right now? You say weird things, fufu.
I see, it was my mistake. I thought she was similar to you.
Really? I see, I guess it was a mistake after all... See ya.
Oh, I was surprised because there was someone who looked like you,▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Ah, sorry. I saw someone who was similar to you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
That so. Oh, I have to go now.
Emm, I felt like I just saw you,▲高嶺＊＊▲, so I was surprised.
Me? I'm sure it was a mistake... See you.
Even if you look at me that much...
Hmm... I think you're too close.
Huh... you don't have to approach that much...
If you look at me that much... Hmm...
You're watching me so much... What's wrong?
You don't have to get that close...
Emm... Isn't this a little too near?
I wonder what I should do...
（I was inadvertently getting close to her）
Yes. But it is you, it is not as surprising.
You can count on me... Ah, it's nothing.
I can count on you after all.
You can't do anything if you fail.
If you care it's not good.
I think it's better not to be depressed.
Don't worry about it each time. Don't change your mind, okay?
...I think we should do what you're thinking.
I see... Hey~, what are you doing?
Ah, Hey~, what are you doing?
I wonder if you can see such wonderful place...
That's right, that's what you chose.
That so... I won't take it.
What is it... Ah, No, don't worry.
Just a little... it's a pity.
How is the job of the library committee? Is it worthwhile?
It's worth doing it... I wonder if that's sounds right...
However, it's good that the number of exchanges increased because of the committee members.
Are the committee members good friends?
Only a handful are on good terms.
Umm... I have something to ask you.
You're doing a part-time job, right? It seems hard, but I think it's worthwhile.
That's right... It can be painful and troublesome, but there are also fun things.
I admire it... the customer service.
Well, it's more like being a friend in part-time job, rather than being a customer.
I want to hear more about it.
Huh, ▲高嶺＊＊▲, are you interested in part-time jobs?
I knew it, after all aren't girls also doing part-time jobs?
And that mean making friends with other girls.
How are you doing in your class? I wonder if you're on good terms with them.
I wonder... I think we are getting good.
Even though you transfered recently, it's amazing.
No, it's amazing. If it was me...
（▲高嶺＊＊▲, you make a good face when laughing...）
I know you live alone. How hard is it?
Amazing, you're a high school student living alone. I wonder how every day is...
Hmm, if you're so interested, want to come and see?
Geez, don't make fun of me...
Huh... I don't mind if you don't want to answer.
You have a good first year student on the library committee.
You have a good senpai at your part-time job.
I see... you are friend with them...
No... it's alright, I think you should have many friends.
I might me be on good terms with them but, I want to be on better terms with you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Ah... that's right. That's good. Yes, I want to get along with you...
Huh... I heard some strange things, so I'm sorry to ask?
I asked the library committee, and they said you get along with a first year.
At you part-time job... I heard you get along with a senpai.
...I knew it... You get along so well?
No. Even if you care, there's no helping it.
I'm sorry. I was just a little worried.
Well, you might say it like that. I speak with you more often,▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Is that so?... Yes, thank you.
Emm... I have something to ask.
Is there a first year student in the library committee you're getting along?
You get along with the senpai at you part-time job, right?
... I knew it. Do you get along so well?
I'm on good terms with you too.
Rather, I speak more with you more, right ▲高嶺＊＊▲? Even now, right?
Fufu, I see. Let's get along okay?
Emm... that... Yes, I was trying saying "Whassup"...
That's right. Trying is important! ...I'm kidding.
Why do you stay with me?
I don't think it's that interesting being with me.
Hmm... It's just that you're here....
It's because you're here. We're together because it's fun.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲, I'm hearing strange things from you...）
I recently wondered if I have changed a little.
I don't think I have changed...
That's right, you've become brighter than before.
Yes, I really feel like that.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲, I wonder where you heard that）
（It's a sports equipment store... I wonder if there's anything that we could use for club activities...）
I don't think it's a coincidence, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Two tennis club members meet at a equipment store... Do you think it's coincidence?
Emm... then we got together with a purpose...
Yes, it's inevitable! Maybe it's fate!
Well, I was just hanging around.
Huh? Ah... Geez, don't tease me.
▲高嶺＊＊▲ you're so serious. Hey, let me know if you have any recommendations.
Yes, I am a serious tennis member, so I will tell you. Fufu.
I often use that kind of thing...
Thank you, I learned something new.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, you seem good at teaching people.
I wonder about that... I don't know.
That's how I started with Yumi-chan... I'm not good nor confident.
Huh, that's how it started ...I wasn't confident I was doing the right thing...
How should I look it it?
Hmmー, I don't think many high school students know the answer... ▲高嶺＊＊▲, isn't your father good at it?
Papa? Yeah... that might be good, I will try to ask.
Thank you for the advide. If Papa teaches me, I might become a spartan... Fufu.
（Spartan...▲高嶺＊＊▲ is seriously going to ask her father）
（There are some cooking utensils over here...）
（I think it might be good to cook for myself...Hmm）
What a coincidence. Are you shopping?
That's right. I've come to buy ingredients to make sweets.
Oh, are you interested in making sweets?
Haha, no way. I can't do those as a man.
I think it's okay for a man...
It doesn't suit me. I'm more interested in the sweets made by you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
That's... it's not a big deal.
You're so humble. ▲高嶺＊＊▲, you're making the face of a pro!
Geez, stop it. If you expect that much, I might be in trouble when giving you some...
Ah~...no, that's not it! Emm, it's...
Ah yes, I'm indebted to everyone in the tennis club... so I thought of giving gifts... I'm kidding.
Eh, that sounds interesting! I'm looking forward to it!
Ah, geez... don't expect that much.
Oops... we talked quite a bit.
Yeah... it was quite a bit.
I'm sorry for bothering you so much. Were you in the middle of doing some shopping?
I't fine, because it's something that can be bought fast.
I see. Then I'll be going now.
Ah yes, I'm looking forward to your sweets!
（Well then, it's time to go back...）
（She's in front of the pet store... I feel I've seen this before）
What are you looking at? The pet shop?
Oh, rabbits? I see, ▲高嶺＊＊▲ loves rabbits.
I love them. Look, aren't they cute?
Sure, there are various kinds of rabbits.
Fufu, that's right. Minirex lop ears... and the Netherlands dwarf!
Yes, lop ear. This Horan lop ear looks a little small, isn't it?
But its face is big and round. And its ears are cute♪
（▲高嶺＊＊▲, sometimes you speak with such emotion...）
With this, we looked at all the small rabbits.
No, it's nothing. Everyone had their own things and were cute.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, do you come here often?
Sometimes. I come everytime I wonder if they have a new rabbit...
I can't keep one, so I feel sorry for the people in the shop, I'm just looking all the time...
Ah, it's time for me to go. Thank you for being with me. See you.
（She's wandering around in front of Winning Burger...）
▲高嶺＊＊▲, want to go to Winning Burger again?
Emm... That's right, I was going home, so this is not a detour.
Haha, you've been addicted to it recently.
That's not true... I've come here from time to time.
I see, since we're here, let's go in together.
I'm sorry, I shouldn't force you.
No, it's fine. I couldn't have achieved my goal alone, but you helped me.
Huh? Emm, well... it was not that, but I really felt I was alone.
Oh, but it was fun. Thank you.
Yes, then I'll see you later.
（Ah, I'm tired. I'll go back home...）
Hey, let's go home. Want to go to Menler?
Oh, Naruto. I want to head home, so how about ramen instead?.
I can do various things living alone.
Oh, are you guys going home together? Then I'll tag along.
Hmm... are you going alone? What about the other girls?
Well, there's have to be a balance between men and women at school!
Would you like to go home together? There aren't enough girls with us.
Huh, I'll be going ahead. See you...
（It looks like she's looking for something... It's hard to speak to her...）
（Entering the store and leaving 3 times... ▲高嶺＊＊▲, what exactly are you doing?）
（I can't do anything, I should go home...）
（It seems she's still doing her things...）
（Entering the store and leaving 3 times... ▲高嶺＊＊▲, what exactly are you doing?）
（I can't do anything, I should go home...）
Ha~a... I knew it, I should stop.
No, this is not what it looks like!
What's not what it looks like?
Let's stop at Winning Burger, it's my treat this time.
Let's eat quickly and the leave the school and go home. Sounds about right?
Fufu... yes, then just a little.
No! I just bought something at the bookstore and...
I'm kidding, so calm down... and, what did you buy?
Ah, is it a leisure information magazine? Are you going somewhere?
I'm doing research for the kid next door. I take him somewhere as a reward for improving his grades.
Oh... And where are you going?
With this magazine, I think it's a good think to go and see beforehand.
I'm taking care of someone else's child, right? So I'll take him next Sunday.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲ is really serious ... Hmm? Maybe...）
Are you going to do it alone?
（I knew it... ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s doing this alone...）
Well then, it's time for me to go. See you.
Whassup, ▲高嶺＊＊▲, another detour I see.
Huh, another leisure information magazine? Did you go to see it before?
Yes... Actually, I haven't been able to decide the place yet.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲, it seems you can't decide yet...）
It's hard, but do your best
It's hard, but do your best!
I was just thinking I'm free on Sunday. Can't I?
But then, from the perspective of others...
You mean it'll look like a date?
